---
title: SDP — System Directed Put Flow
---
flowchart TD
    START([Worker opens SDP\nsrc/pages/SDPPage.tsx]) --> S1

    S1[State: entry\naisleField auto-focuses\nSize override: all roles\nStorage Code/Zone override: IM+ only]

    S1 --> AISLE[Worker enters Aisle number\nhandleAisleConfirm\nfocus moves to palletField]

    AISLE --> PALLET_SCAN{Scan Pallet ID\nhandlePalletScan}

    PALLET_SCAN --> VALIDATE{Aisle entered?}
    VALIDATE -->|No aisle| NOOP[Field disabled\nno action]
    VALIDATE -->|Aisle present| API_DIR

    API_DIR[POST /api/puts/directed\napi/functions/puts.ts — directedPut\ncheckPalletEligibility\nresolveEffectiveCriteria\nStorage Code/Size exact-match, Zone soft-pref\nfindNextLocation — zone asc, bin desc, level asc\nwith Zone-1 fallback retry\nCreate Reservation row incl. wasStaged]

    API_DIR --> DIR_OK{Result?}
    DIR_OK -->|PALLET_NOT_FOUND| ERR_P1[Error: Pallet not found\npalletField kept — re-focused for retry]
    DIR_OK -->|CANCELED| ERR_P4[Error: Pallet canceled\npalletField kept — re-focused for retry]
    DIR_OK -->|BLOCKED_BY_PENDING_PULL| ERR_P5[Error: Open Label pending\npalletField kept — re-focused for retry]
    DIR_OK -->|NO_CARTONS| ERR_P2[Error: No stored cartons\npalletField kept — re-focused for retry]
    DIR_OK -->|NO_LOCATIONS| ERR_P3[Error: No eligible locations\nin requested aisle\npalletField kept — re-focused for retry]
    DIR_OK -->|OK| DIR_RESULT[Returns reservationId\ndirectedLocation\npallet details\nalreadyStored flag]

    ERR_P1 --> S1
    ERR_P4 --> S1
    ERR_P5 --> S1
    ERR_P2 --> S1
    ERR_P3 --> S1

    DIR_RESULT --> MOVE_CHECK{alreadyStored?}
    MOVE_CHECK -->|Yes + consolidating| INFO_MSG[Info: move scenario\nshown in message bar]
    MOVE_CHECK -->|Yes, not consolidating| WARN_MSG[Warning: move scenario\nshown in message bar]
    MOVE_CHECK -->|No| S2

    INFO_MSG --> S2
    WARN_MSG --> S2

    S2[State: directed\nScreen LOCKED — active reservation\ndirectedLocation shown in red\nConfirm Location — full 3-box Aisle/Bin/Level panel\nauto-focuses first box\n5-min server-side timer pushes expiry to screen\nvia polling, not on next scan attempt]

    S2 --> ACTION{Worker action?}

    ACTION -->|Confirm Location\n3-box entry or scan\nhandleLocationConfirm| CONF[POST /api/puts/:id/confirm\napi/functions/puts.ts — confirmPut\nvalidate scanned === directed\nplacePallet atomic transaction\ncopies storageCode/size/zone onto pallet\ndelete Reservation\nwriteLog PUT or MOVE_PUT incl. wasStaged + verification]

    CONF --> CONF_OK{Result?}
    CONF_OK -->|LOCATION_MISMATCH| ERR_C1[Error: Wrong location\nfields cleared + re-focused]
    CONF_OK -->|NOT_FOUND\nreservation expired| EXPIRE_C[Warning: Reservation expired\nfull reset to entry]
    CONF_OK -->|OK, wasStaged true| PUT_SUCCESS_STAGED[Success: Put / Move complete — Staged\ninfo tone\nstopPolling\nhistory outcome → PUT or MOVE]
    CONF_OK -->|OK, wasStaged false| PUT_SUCCESS_EMPTY[Success: Put / Move complete — Empty\nwarning tone, still Info-blue message\nstopPolling\nhistory outcome → PUT or MOVE]

    ERR_C1 --> S2

    ACTION -->|Unassign button\nhandleUnassign| UNASSIGN[POST /api/puts/:id/unassign\napi/functions/puts.ts — unassignPut\nrestore location to STAGED if wasStaged===true, else EMPTY\ndelete Reservation atomic]

    UNASSIGN --> UN_OK{Result?}
    UN_OK -->|NOT_FOUND| EXPIRE_U[Warning: Reservation expired\nfull reset]
    UN_OK -->|OK| UN_SUCCESS[Info: Reservation cleared — Staged/Empty shown\nhistory outcome → RELEASED\nreset to entry — locked overrides kept]

    ACTION -->|Blocked Put button\nhandleBlock| BLOCK[POST /api/puts/:id/block\napi/functions/puts.ts — blockPut\nHold Both on current location\nrestore to STAGED if wasStaged===true, else EMPTY\nre-derive resolveEffectiveCriteria\nfindNextLocation\nnew Reservation carries wasStaged forward\nwriteLog RESERVE]

    BLOCK --> BLK_OK{Result?}
    BLK_OK -->|NO_LOCATIONS| ERR_BLK[Error: No further locations\nhold placed\nfull reset to entry]
    BLK_OK -->|NOT_FOUND| EXPIRE_B[Warning: Reservation expired\nfull reset]
    BLK_OK -->|OK| BLK_SUCCESS[New reservationId + directedLocation\nupdate directed state\nold entry → BLOCKED\nnew entry → ASSIGNED\nconfirm panel re-focused]

    BLK_SUCCESS --> S2

    PUT_SUCCESS_STAGED --> RESET_N[Partial reset\nclear pallet + confirm\nnon-locked overrides cleared\nfocus → pallet field]
    PUT_SUCCESS_EMPTY --> RESET_N
    RESET_N --> S1

    UN_SUCCESS --> S1
    EXPIRE_C --> S1_FULL[Full reset — all fields cleared\nfocus → aisle field]
    EXPIRE_U --> S1_FULL
    EXPIRE_B --> S1_FULL
    ERR_BLK --> S1_FULL
    S1_FULL --> S1

